  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `erigon version 2.43.0-stable-1106475e`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\nErigon Command (with flags/config):\r\n\r\n```\r\n      - erigon\r\n      - --private.api.addr\r\n      - 0.0.0.0:9090\r\n      - --datadir\r\n      - /var/lib/erigon\r\n      - --port\r\n      - ${EL_P2P_PORT:-30303}\r\n      - --p2p.allowed-ports\r\n      - ${EL_P2P_PORT:-30303},${ERIGON_P2P_PORT_2:-30304},${ERIGON_P2P_PORT_3:-30305}\r\n      - --torrent.port\r\n      - ${ERIGON_TORRENT_PORT:-42069}\r\n      - --nat\r\n      - any\r\n      - --chain\r\n      - ${NETWORK}\r\n      - --log.console.verbosity\r\n      - ${LOG_LEVEL}\r\n      - --metrics\r\n      - --metrics.addr\r\n      - 0.0.0.0\r\n      - --http\r\n      - --http.addr\r\n      - 0.0.0.0\r\n      - --http.port\r\n      - ${EL_RPC_PORT}\r\n      - --http.vhosts=*\r\n      - --http.corsdomain=*\r\n      - --http.api\r\n      - web3,eth,net,engine\r\n      - --ws\r\n      # Allow RocketPool >=1.9 watchtower queries\r\n      - --rpc.returndata.limit\r\n      - \"1000000\"\r\n      - --authrpc.addr\r\n      - 0.0.0.0\r\n      - --authrpc.port\r\n      - ${EE_PORT:-8551}\r\n      - --authrpc.vhosts=*\r\n      - --authrpc.jwtsecret\r\n      - /var/lib/erigon/ee-secret/jwtsecret\r\n      - --maxpeers\r\n      - ${EL_MAX_PEER_COUNT:-100}\r\n      # To assist with recordsize 16k in ZFS\r\n      - --db.pagesize\r\n      - 16K\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nConcensus Layer: `Lighthouse v4.1.0-693886b`\r\n\r\nConcensus Layer Command (with flags/config):\r\n\r\n```\r\n      - lighthouse\r\n      - bn\r\n      - --disable-upnp\r\n      - --datadir\r\n      - /var/lib/lighthouse\r\n      - --http\r\n      - --http-address\r\n      - 0.0.0.0\r\n      - --http-port\r\n      - ${CL_REST_PORT:-5052}\r\n      - --network\r\n      - ${NETWORK}\r\n      - --port\r\n      - ${CL_P2P_PORT:-9000}\r\n      - --target-peers\r\n      - ${CL_MAX_PEER_COUNT:-80}\r\n      - --execution-endpoint\r\n      - ${EL_NODE}\r\n      - --execution-jwt\r\n      - /var/lib/lighthouse/beacon/ee-secret/jwtsecret\r\n      - --debug-level=${LOG_LEVEL}\r\n      - --metrics\r\n      - --metrics-address\r\n      - 0.0.0.0\r\n      - --metrics-port\r\n      - \"8008\"\r\n      - --validator-monitor-auto\r\n      - --suggested-fee-recipient\r\n      - ${FEE_RECIPIENT}\r\n```\r\n\r\nChain/Network: mainnet\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl https://cl.example.com/eth/v2/beacon/blocks/6211679 && echo\r\n{\"code\":500,\"message\":\"UNHANDLED_ERROR: BlockHashMissingFromExecutionLayer(0x66a2a7245aad3b8249277de493909ef568353a530babc44da395687322591b4d)\",\"stacktraces\":[]}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Context\r\n\r\nThe same query against a Lighthouse connected to Nethermind succeeds. It's a Lighthouse connected to Erigon that fails.\r\n",
